longBusinessSummary: Vestiage, Inc. engages in fitness event planning business. The company offers event planning services to fitness gyms. It also sponsors competitions within local communities, as well as organize events, such as parties and educational seminars. In addition, it offers vendor organization; food services; securing competition equipment; and volunteers to work for the event. The company was formerly known as Empire Pizza Holdings, Inc. and changed its name to Vestiage, Inc. in March 2013. Vestiage, Inc. is based in Scottsdale, Arizona.
